_sText:
This fightyard map is on behalf of The Red Star's TS3/CS:S community: "Settle 4 Nothing" or "S4N" for short. It's a very simple, symmetrical zone illuminated by intense red lighting. Great for 1v1s, 2v2s, and 3v3s (Supports a maximum of 12, 6 on each team).

Have lots of fun and let me know what you think!

~The Red Star, Settle4Nothing Owner

Let me know if you want to join Settle4Nothing's teamspeak server or CS:S Fightyard Server.

Message me here: http://steamcommunity.com/id/mgtheredstar/
